casebody.data:
DAYSTAR SELLER FINANCING, LLC, Plaintiff/Counterdefendant-Appellee,
v.
Patrick HUNDLEY, Defendant/Counterplaintiff/Third-Party Plaintiff-Appellant,
and
David Byker, Counterdefendant/Third-Party Defendant-Appellee,
and
Jaco Rentals, LLC, Lost Beach Properties, LLC, and Byker & Associates, Inc., Third-Party Defendants-Appellees. SC: 158664
COA: 339467 Supreme Court of Michigan. June 12, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the September 27, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
